{"id": "1486705527378411601", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "578599324007792641", "author_name": "tentensandayo", "author_bot": false, "content": "シルバーコアを何に使うかで悩んでいます\n現状のパーティにはとても満足していて、今後もしばらくは似たパーティで進めるつもりです\nそこでシルバーコアを運命の札ガチャなどに回してしまうべきか、キャラの凸を狙うべきかで悩んでいます", "timestamp": "2026-03-26T12:36:59.380000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1486705527097659433", "filename": "IMG_5558.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 150496, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1391701560496623688/1486705527097659433/IMG_5558.jpg?ex=6a33e66b&is=6a3294eb&hm=5c380a93f88fd88762545161c6aa4928a57eb2c123e9841e725b51fcd8ac52b3&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
