{"id": "1486677730476167178", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "1155282626668662816", "author_name": "ya.ma.00", "author_bot": false, "content": "特異点のビーコンはこの式でいうとeにあたると言う認識ですがあってますか？\n特異点のビーコン25を獲得するとかかれてれば、eに25を代入すればよいでしょうか？", "timestamp": "2026-03-26T10:46:32.082000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["730374482522406972"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1486157896952578089", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1486677893915349043", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1410178662933987368", "author_name": "satansukisuki", "author_bot": false, "content": "方向性の質問なのですが、微課金でやっていく場合、石の使い方は\n・１つのパーティの凸を進める\n・複数のパーティの為にキャラ確保する\nのどちらが良いでしょうか？", "timestamp": "2026-03-26T10:47:11.049000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1486678037746684014", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "730374482522406972", "author_name": "kuroneko4253", "author_bot": false, "content": "俺もそういう認識だけど違うという説もあり…", "timestamp": "2026-03-26T10:47:45.341000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-03-26T10:47:51.568000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1155282626668662816"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1486677730476167178", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1486678444292177990", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "1126482815610011721", "author_name": "anonymous.409", "author_bot": false, "content": "ストーリーを進めていくと融災禁区と言うものが解放されるのですが､その攻略に同じキャラを使うことは出来ません｡\n最低でも20体のキャラを育成しなければいけないため､恒常でも強いキャラは多く確保しておきたいところですねー", "timestamp": "2026-03-26T10:49:22.269000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-03-26T10:53:40.539000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1410178662933987368"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1486677893915349043", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1486679308801146900", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "1155282626668662816", "author_name": "ya.ma.00", "author_bot": false, "content": "そうなんですか！\nいずれにしろ教えていただきありがとうございます😊", "timestamp": "2026-03-26T10:52:48.384000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["730374482522406972"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1486678037746684014", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1486680684490915920", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "1410178662933987368", "author_name": "satansukisuki", "author_bot": false, "content": "ありがとうございます！\n確かに融災は2パーティしか無いのでいつも取り逃がしています…\n\nただ狂魔メインで使っててタイス復刻が来てたのでどうしようかなと。\n融災は触れず幻夢の深奥？などの単パーティで済みそうなのオンリーもありなのかなって思ったんですよね笑", "timestamp": "2026-03-26T10:58:16.374000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1126482815610011721"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1486678444292177990", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1486681949954379878", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "1126482815610011721", "author_name": "anonymous.409", "author_bot": false, "content": "成程！確かに限定キャラの場合は無闇に頭数を揃えるより､サルバやタイスなどの強キャラの凸を進めた方が融災でも幻夢でも強い場合が多いです｡ただ恒常は､普段使いしないようでも､ヘロットやジェンキンなどの強キャラを幅広く揃えて(出来れば凸も)おきたいところだと思ってます！", "timestamp": "2026-03-26T11:03:18.084000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1410178662933987368"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1486680684490915920", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1486683987480154243", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "1410178662933987368", "author_name": "satansukisuki", "author_bot": false, "content": "やっぱリソースは絞った方が良さそうですかね！\n恒常は初期から触ってるのでそこそこです。限定の石、凸素材をどこに使うかが悩みです…\nただ、タイスやザルバに舵をきるのも凸数結構いりそうで勇気必要で笑…めちゃ強いフレンド枠のタイス、ザルバも多いのもあって…", "timestamp": "2026-03-26T11:11:23.868000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1126482815610011721"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1486681949954379878", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1486687776547016866", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "452490393812992000", "author_name": "alcoholic0908", "author_bot": false, "content": "タイスどうしても引きたくて6章までのシルバーコア全部溶かしてしまった　余らせたら札セットガチャ重ねようと思ってたのに……", "timestamp": "2026-03-26T11:26:27.252000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1486687888631660554", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "576787429231558676", "author_name": "kerokuma", "author_bot": false, "content": "こんばんは、始めて2週間程の初心者です。\n微課金でちまちまとストーリーを進めていたのですが6章辺りで詰まってしまって…\n今は育成を頑張ろうとしているのですが、まずは60レベルまで何とかしようと思ったのですが、何もかもが足りなさすぎる…！\nそこで、皆さんはどうやって経験値素材や薔薇金券を調達していますか…？\n是非ご教授の程よろしくお願いいたします！", "timestamp": "2026-03-26T11:26:53.975000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1486688688363667556", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "763468659863584799", "author_name": "sugoitsubasanohaetaop", "author_bot": false, "content": "基本的に素材や金券は今開催されているソレールイベントみたいなタイプで回収する人が多いと思います。\nそれ以外のコンテンツでは一切エルフェリンは使いません。", "timestamp": "2026-03-26T11:30:04.646000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["576787429231558676"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👈", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1486687888631660554", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1486688829057536011", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "452490393812992000", "author_name": "alcoholic0908", "author_bot": false, "content": "同じく初心者ですが、経験値素材については今やってる復刻イベントの1幕を救援借りて回した方が実入りがいいと気付いたとこです。", "timestamp": "2026-03-26T11:30:38.190000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["576787429231558676"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1486687888631660554", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1486689268285050880", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "763468659863584799", "author_name": "sugoitsubasanohaetaop", "author_bot": false, "content": "私も素材貯めてる方では無いとは思いますが、エルフェリンパス買ってたらそれを消化するだけで常にこのくらいのストックにはなります", "timestamp": "2026-03-26T11:32:22.910000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1486689267861164172", "filename": "Screenshot_20260326-203117.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1714614, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1391701560496623688/1486689267861164172/Screenshot_20260326-203117.png?ex=6a33d746&is=6a3285c6&hm=5ad6189f8810b6a53b1e8fda8a1e6817eb686dc3dad0671688abe163a46607c7&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1486689544941076641", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "576787429231558676", "author_name": "kerokuma", "author_bot": false, "content": "なるほど…！お二方ともありがとうございます！\n既にイベント外で溶かしてしまったエルフェリンに想いを馳せつつ全力でソレール様に貢いできます…！", "timestamp": "2026-03-26T11:33:28.870000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1486689660276047954", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "576787429231558676", "author_name": "kerokuma", "author_bot": false, "content": "見たことのない桁数でお目目が飛び出ました\nこうなれるように精進します", "timestamp": "2026-03-26T11:33:56.368000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["763468659863584799"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1486689268285050880", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1486689846498951179", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "763468659863584799", "author_name": "sugoitsubasanohaetaop", "author_bot": false, "content": "これは好きな界域とかも絡むので好みですが、金券のアイテム交換で毎日このくらいのは買ってる", "timestamp": "2026-03-26T11:34:40.767000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1486689846469722216", "filename": "Screenshot_20260326-203336.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1804414, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1391701560496623688/1486689846469722216/Screenshot_20260326-203336.png?ex=6a33d7d0&is=6a328650&hm=e7c27146fafe3fffaad770c3b2e6d29acf89d0cac37f548b44db9f4c0b830e15&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1486689985686929490", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "763468659863584799", "author_name": "sugoitsubasanohaetaop", "author_bot": false, "content": "結構素材とか貯める人は更新してドカ買いしてるみたい", "timestamp": "2026-03-26T11:35:13.952000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👀", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1486690222178570260", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1416069614743326892", "author_name": "chamaru0325_53858", "author_bot": false, "content": "一応リリース初日からやってるはずなのにここめちゃくちゃ勉強になる…ありがとうございます", "timestamp": "2026-03-26T11:36:10.336000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1486690874225201245", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "763468659863584799", "author_name": "sugoitsubasanohaetaop", "author_bot": false, "content": "イベントのキャラと札の凸が進んでる場合はイベント通貨の獲得効率が良かったはずなので、そこで薬剤とかぶっぱして全部金券に変えると数千万は貯まるはずです", "timestamp": "2026-03-26T11:38:45.796000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
